    under the terms of this License.

6.3 The Copyright Holders' Collective commits not to relicense this
    Software or its contributions under a more restrictive license.
    Any license change requires unanimous consent of all
    Maintainers before taking effect.
    No license change may weaken any provision
    of Article 3 (Cognitive Sovereignty Protection).

